These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, tram, roller
1. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | roller | boat | scooter | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, chess, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | collecting | fishing | camping | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, musician, electrician, pilot
1. the musician is on the right of the electrician##1
2. the musician is on the far left or far right##3
3. the lawyer is the lawyer##1
4. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | pilot | lawyer | electrician | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
