.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, sports, romance
1. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching sports movies##2
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire | romance | disaster |

