.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, dancing, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | fishing | dancing | puzzles |

