2. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
3. the malaysian is between the pakistani and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani | malaysian | mexican |

