3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | van | skateboard | car |

