.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, goldfish, fish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | fish | chinchilla | mouse | goldfish |

